00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,377
Your Majesty.

291
00:20:04,711 --> 00:20:08,044
Water Immortal is anxiously
longing for Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir.

292
00:20:08,622 --> 00:20:10,266
