293
00:20:11,022 --> 00:20:12,577
But as Leader Yin Que said,

294
00:20:13,422 --> 00:20:15,288
if Fire Immortal’s soul is still alive,

295
00:20:15,288 --> 00:20:16,755
with Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir,

