00:21:22,088 --> 00:21:23,377
The Light of Xuanqiong

313
00:21:23,822 --> 00:21:26,977
actually needs to be borne
by Water Immortal’s body.

314
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,977
Due to the strong light,

315
00:21:28,977 --> 00:21:30,844
I’m afraid her body has been melted.

316
00:21:31,111 --> 00:21:34,000
