317
00:21:34,222 --> 00:21:38,222
I’m afraid she can only stay alive for some time.

318
00:21:42,888 --> 00:21:43,777
You should be leaving.

319
00:21:44,266 --> 00:21:44,933
Yes.

320
00:22:11,155 --> 00:22:11,866
Mi,

321
00:22:13,288 --> 00:22:15,111
I will find the way to save you.

322
00:22:53,540 --> 00:22:55,421
"Mengtuo Scripture"

323
00:22:58,133 --> 00:22:59,200
Blood Ball.

324
00:23:00,311 --> 00:23:01,644
Change fate against God’s will.

325
00:23:28,933 --> 00:23:29,511
Mi,

326
00:23:30,888 --> 00:23:32,577
since you are my inexorable doom,

327
00:23:33,688 --> 00:23:34,533
now

328
00:23:36,222 --> 00:23:37,333
I come to accept it.

329
00:24:38,533 --> 00:24:39,466
Your Majesty,

330
00:24:41,688 --> 00:24:42,533
what are you doing?

331
00:24:43,022 --> 00:24:43,955
Leave!

332
00:24:44,488 --> 00:24:45,422
Your Majesty,

333
00:24:46,222 --> 00:24:47,866
now the demon army is about to attack.

334
00:24:48,577 --> 00:24:49,644
If you hurt yourself,

335
00:24:49,866 --> 00:24:50,622
how can Heaven Realm...

336
00:24:52,000 --> 00:24:54,266
