359
00:26:09,066 --> 00:26:10,577
Though I don’t want to irritate him,

360
00:26:11,022 --> 00:26:13,377
I really can’t bear this.

361
00:26:14,666 --> 00:26:16,400
If you are not willing to fight with me,

362
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,555
I won’t force you.

363
00:26:22,444 --> 00:26:24,488
