364
00:26:24,666 --> 00:26:25,555
No matter what happens,

365
00:26:25,555 --> 00:26:27,466
I will share weal and woe with you.

366
00:26:58,933 --> 00:26:59,644
Your Majesty.

367
00:27:04,533 --> 00:27:05,333
I am fine.

368
00:27:17,066 --> 00:27:18,222
Your Majesty.

369
00:27:18,755 --> 00:27:19,688
Did you use…

370
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:22,088
Do not let Jin Mi know this.

371
00:27:22,888 --> 00:27:23,688
But…

372
00:27:23,688 --> 00:27:25,600
This is a forbidden magic of Heaven Realm.

373
00:27:27,288 --> 00:27:28,400
I am Heavenly Emperor.

374
00:27:29,777 --> 00:27:31,555
If this matter is known by others,

375
00:27:32,044 --> 00:27:33,288
I’m afraid there will be
changes in the six realms,

376
00:27:35,644 --> 00:27:36,666
and Mi will be gossiped

377
00:27:38,088 --> 00:27:39,644
by others.

378
00:27:40,933 --> 00:27:41,866
Remember.

379
00:27:43,911 --> 00:27:46,177
Do not let others know this.

380
00:27:47,155 --> 00:27:47,911
Understand?

381
00:27:49,155 --> 00:27:50,311
I understand.

382
00:27:53,777 --> 00:27:54,444
Your Majesty.

383
00:27:57,066 --> 00:27:59,466
Drink this bowl of decoction
to nourish your body.

384
00:28:24,044 --> 00:28:24,755
Phoenix.

385
00:28:26,533 --> 00:28:27,511
Phoenix.

386
00:28:28,355 --> 00:28:29,688
Phoenix.

387
00:28:36,177 --> 00:28:38,311
Water Immortal, you are awake.

388
00:28:39,688 --> 00:28:41,600
Kuang Lu, what happened?

389
00:28:42,533 --> 00:28:43,128
Yesterday,

390
00:28:43,128 --> 00:28:45,955
you injected the Light of
Xuanqiong into Jiuzhuan Golden Elixir.

391
00:28:46,755 --> 00:28:49,333
You were injured as
you couldn’t bear the strength

392
00:28:49,777 --> 00:28:50,577
of the Light of Xuanqiong.

393
00:28:51,733 --> 00:28:52,711
Luckily, His Majesty,

394
00:28:53,688 --> 00:28:54,444
His Majesty

395
00:28:54,444 --> 00:28:55,600
transferred some magic power to you

396
00:28:56,044 --> 00:28:57,555
and thus saved you.

397
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,733
You can recover in a few days.

398
00:29:00,800 --> 00:29:02,355
His Majesty transferred
some magic power to me?

399
00:29:03,333 --> 00:29:04,444
How is he now?

400
00:29:05,511 --> 00:29:06,577
His Majesty is fine.

401
00:29:06,888 --> 00:29:08,355
Just now immortals have things to report,

402
00:29:08,711 --> 00:29:10,311
so he is occupied now.

403
00:29:10,311 --> 00:29:11,777
He will come to see you some time later.

404
00:29:14,933 --> 00:29:16,044
Have a cup of tea.

405
00:29:16,800 --> 00:29:17,866
Thanks.

406
00:29:19,600 --> 00:29:20,266
Immortal,

407
00:29:22,177 --> 00:29:23,333
can you keep

408
00:29:24,622 --> 00:29:26,000
the next conversations

409
00:29:26,222 --> 00:29:27,333
between you and me?

410
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:30,800
Go ahead.

411
00:29:31,511 --> 00:29:32,400
Is your heart

412
00:29:33,866 --> 00:29:35,066
made of ice?

413
00:29:36,888 --> 00:29:38,222
Even if it is made of ice,

414
00:29:39,866 --> 00:29:43,200
as His Majesty paid for you time and time again,

415
00:29:43,733 --> 00:29:45,555
your heart should have melted.

416
00:29:49,822 --> 00:29:50,755
Immortal,

417
00:29:51,333 --> 00:29:52,488
I beg you.

418
00:29:52,755 --> 00:29:53,688
I beg you

419
00:29:53,955 --> 00:29:55,600
to show more feelings for His Majesty, OK?

420
00:29:56,222 --> 00:29:58,311
You can lie to him or temporize.

421
00:29:59,466 --> 00:30:00,533
It will be better than

422
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,400
make him sad

423
00:30:05,911 --> 00:30:07,644
and bitterly disappointed day and night.

424
00:30:09,288 --> 00:30:11,200
I have feelings for His Majesty,

425
00:30:13,022 --> 00:30:14,800
but that’s not what he wants.

426
00:30:15,777 --> 00:30:17,644
If I lie to him or temporize,

427
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,511
pretending to love him very much,

428
00:30:21,422 --> 00:30:23,244
that will hurt him more.

429
00:30:23,911 --> 00:30:24,800
Just like you.

430
00:30:25,377 --> 00:30:27,377
If I ask you to pretend

431
00:30:29,111 --> 00:30:30,888
to be indifferent to His Majesty,

432
00:30:31,377 --> 00:30:32,533
can you do it?

433
00:30:36,533 --> 00:30:37,911
Why did you say so?

434
00:30:38,888 --> 00:30:40,311
His Majesty is so distinguished

435
00:30:40,711 --> 00:30:42,622
that I can never think of that.

436
00:30:42,933 --> 00:30:43,822
Kuang Lu,

437
00:30:44,222 --> 00:30:45,377
take it easy.

438
00:30:45,911 --> 00:30:46,977
I don’t mean to blame you.

439
00:30:47,866 --> 00:30:48,844
In fact,

440
00:30:50,133 --> 00:30:51,422
you and I are the same.

441
00:30:52,622 --> 00:30:54,222
We both know in heart

442
00:30:54,577 --> 00:30:56,088
we can’t be with the ones we love,

443
00:30:58,444 --> 00:31:00,533
but we can’t cheat our hearts.

444
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:03,777
I promise you.

445
00:31:04,177 --> 00:31:05,733
No one else

446
00:31:06,355 --> 00:31:08,933
will know our conversations today.

447
00:31:09,511 --> 00:31:10,666
Don’t worry.

448
00:31:12,755 --> 00:31:13,733
Thank you, Water Immortal.

449
00:31:14,488 --> 00:31:15,866
I’ll be leaving.

450
00:31:24,755 --> 00:31:26,977
Yesterday, I was injured
by the Light of Xuanqionge,

451
00:31:28,133 --> 00:31:29,555
but I am fine today.

452
00:31:29,911 --> 00:31:31,733
How can I recover so fast?

453
00:31:35,244 --> 00:31:36,977
What is your color?

454
00:31:52,355 --> 00:31:53,111
Your Majesty.

455
00:31:53,866 --> 00:31:54,711
Has she woken up?

456
00:31:55,600 --> 00:31:56,444
I told her that

457
00:31:56,888 --> 00:31:59,111
Your Majesty was fine and
had gone to discuss matters with others,

458
00:31:59,822 --> 00:32:02,444
and would go to see her later.

459
00:32:11,244 --> 00:32:12,000
Your Majesty,

460
00:32:12,933 --> 00:32:16,044
Blood Ball will consume half of your life.

461
00:32:16,666 --> 00:32:18,000
Is it worthy

462
00:32:18,533 --> 00:32:19,777
to do this?

463
00:32:22,844 --> 00:32:25,377
Has Immortal Tai Si joined with Lord Po Jun?

464
00:32:27,911 --> 00:32:28,622
OK.

465
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:31,333
Tell him

466
00:32:31,822 --> 00:32:33,022
once the war begins,

467
00:32:34,044 --> 00:32:35,333
I will show up.

468
00:32:35,955 --> 00:32:36,800
Your Majesty,

469
00:32:37,377 --> 00:32:38,755
you are weak now

470
00:32:39,111 --> 00:32:40,311
and need rest.

471
00:32:40,977 --> 00:32:42,355
If you go to the battlefield now,

472
00:32:43,866 --> 00:32:44,888
it’ll be too dangerous.

473
00:32:45,777 --> 00:32:47,333
Since I took this position,

474
00:32:49,111 --> 00:32:50,711
I have to be responsible for Heaven Realm.

475
00:32:52,755 --> 00:32:53,333
Your Majesty.

476
00:33:19,466 --> 00:33:20,755
Supreme Lord Lao.

477
00:33:24,577 --> 00:33:25,866
Water Immortal.

478
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:29,688
Yesterday, you almost died yesterday.

479
00:33:30,488 --> 00:33:33,733
How can you recover so fast?

480
00:33:35,377 --> 00:33:36,533
I almost died?

481
00:33:37,333 --> 00:33:38,177
So serious?

482
00:33:39,066 --> 00:33:42,355
Do you have any elixir to cure me?

483
00:33:42,622 --> 00:33:43,600
Water Immortal,

484
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:45,555
I don’t have any elixir

485
00:33:45,822 --> 00:33:48,355
