forbidden magic are recorded.

491
00:34:02,444 --> 00:34:04,977
I seem to hear of

492
00:34:05,777 --> 00:34:08,177
a kind of magic named Blood Ball

493
00:34:08,755 --> 00:34:10,222
which can change fate.

494
00:34:10,755 --> 00:34:11,688
But…

495
00:34:11,688 --> 00:34:12,711
But what?

496
00:34:13,244 --> 00:34:16,888
According to the book,

497
00:34:17,333 --> 00:34:18,933
the rescuer needs to
cut seven sinews and vessels

498
00:34:19,777 --> 00:34:21,911
to inject half essence in his body

499
00:34:21,911 --> 00:34:23,511
into the blood

500
00:34:23,822 --> 00:34:25,155
to make Blood Ball

501
00:34:25,733 --> 00:34:26,622
to feed the injured.

502
00:34:27,155 --> 00:34:28,711
The rescuer

503
00:34:28,711 --> 00:34:32,577
will consume half of his life.

504
00:35:06,133 --> 00:35:06,622
Mi.

505
00:35:09,644 --> 00:35:11,111
You seldom come to my room.

506
00:35:12,622 --> 00:35:13,777
What do you come here for?

507
00:35:23,244 --> 00:35:24,577
Have you ever heard of

508
00:35:25,422 --> 00:35:26,888
the magic Blood Ball?

509
00:35:27,555 --> 00:35:28,666
If you didn’t make Blood Ball,

510
00:35:29,466 --> 00:35:30,666
how would you be injured,

511
00:35:32,311 --> 00:35:33,777
and how would I be safe?

512
00:35:36,311 --> 00:35:37,288
That’s not true.

513
00:35:37,911 --> 00:35:39,200
Where did you hear this?

514
00:35:40,133 --> 00:35:41,955
No one will use such
evil magic in Heaven Realm.

515
00:35:42,755 --> 00:35:44,044
You were not seriously injured yesterday.

516
00:35:44,755 --> 00:35:46,355
