517
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:48,355
OK.

518
00:35:48,711 --> 00:35:49,777
Since you don’t admit it,

519
00:35:50,266 --> 00:35:52,177
I’m going to call Immortal Qihuang.

520
00:35:52,622 --> 00:35:53,155
Mi.

521
00:35:55,644 --> 00:35:56,977
Are you insane?

522
00:35:57,155 --> 00:35:58,533
Do you know

523
00:35:58,711 --> 00:36:00,711
