528
00:36:11,022 --> 00:36:12,088
There is also Blood Ball.

529
00:36:12,977 --> 00:36:15,155
Did you never read Mengtuo Scripture?

530
00:36:16,088 --> 00:36:16,888
Do you doubt

531
00:36:18,666 --> 00:36:19,955
I made you misunderstand Xu Feng?

532
00:36:21,466 --> 00:36:23,600
Even if there was someone playing a trick,

533
00:36:25,066 --> 00:36:26,000
it must be the one

534
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,777
who killed your father.

535
00:36:34,088 --> 00:36:34,888
Mi,

536
00:36:37,066 --> 00:36:38,355
I didn’t know Blood Ball

537
00:36:39,288 --> 00:36:41,200
is also the forbidden magic
recorded in Mengtuo Scripture.

538
00:36:42,266 --> 00:36:43,244
After my mother died,

539
00:36:43,911 --> 00:36:45,200
I brought some remains of hers

540
00:36:45,600 --> 00:36:47,333
to Heaven Realm from Dongting Lake.

541
00:36:47,777 --> 00:36:49,022
Blood Ball

542
00:36:49,511 --> 00:36:51,600
is a kind of magic recorded by my mother.

543
00:36:52,622 --> 00:36:53,777
I didn’t know whether it was true.

544
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:57,511
You were in danger,

545
00:36:58,222 --> 00:36:59,644
so I had to have a try.

546
00:37:00,755 --> 00:37:01,911
Even if I died,

547
00:37:03,555 --> 00:37:05,200
it was a worthy death.

548
00:37:05,955 --> 00:37:08,844
Back then, Lord Puchi saved me,

549
00:37:10,844 --> 00:37:12,533
and I paid him back with 1,000 years of magic power.

550
00:37:14,444 --> 00:37:15,288
Now,

551
00:37:16,844 --> 00:37:18,977
you have given me half of your life.

552
00:37:21,288 --> 00:37:22,844
How can I pay you back?

553
00:37:23,022 --> 00:37:24,355
I don’t need that.

554
00:37:28,577 --> 00:37:29,511
Mi,

555
00:37:30,044 --> 00:37:31,511
as long as I can watch you

556
00:37:32,444 --> 00:37:34,044
and be at your side,

557
00:37:34,888 --> 00:37:35,955
that is enough.

558
00:37:37,200 --> 00:37:39,288
